Output docs/assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful

Type "aigate check crossenv --skip-ai"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "aigate check cross-env --skip-ai"
Enter
